data.description: THIS HOME HAS A VA LOAN THAT IS ASSUMABLE FOR ALL BORROWERS, NOT JUST VETERANS.  2.875% RATE, CALL LISTING AGENT FOR DETAILS! Welcome to this better than new home in Mead where you can still enjoy a small town feel and be close to shoppng and I25.  Here you'll find a well kept and clean three bed + loft, three bath, two-story home that is ready to move into.  The main level offers an open kitchen and great room that are filled with sunlight where it's easy to live and entertain in.  You'll love the stunning white cabinets and granit counters with a large island that functions as a table and the easy flow to the spacious great room.  The dining space is large and can easily fit seating for 10! Head upstairs to find the loft, two secondary bedrooms that share a full bath, the laundry room and the spacious primary with a 5 piece bath and walk-in clostet. If outside is where you want to be, both the front and back yards a great.  Enjoy a glass of wine on the covered front porch that overlooks the grassy open space or head outback to the oversized patio and yard that are big enough to play some games and bbq.  All appliances included AND solar to be paid off at closing by seller!!! Two hours notice to show.
